translated: Kindbom, Axel, merchant, Karlsborg, b. 26/9/66 in Undenäs, Ska-rab. 1., son of Carl Johan K. and Maria Jonsson. Married in 92 to Willielmina Andersson. Children: Kerstin b. 92, Martha b. 94, Carl-Axel b. 98.—Owns a hardware store in Karlsborg since 93. Former member of the municipal council, former chairman of the local savings bank in Skaraborg county, former county official and former board member of the Skaraborg Individual Bank branch in Karlsborg, board member of the Soldiers' Home, the Karlsborg electrical distribution association, and the Forsviks Bruk company. Owns and operates Tyssingen estate in Mölltorp parish. Awarded the Royal Order of Vasa in 1933.
